lead_paragraph: DeAndre Jordan scored 20 points on 7-for-7 shooting, Chris Paul had 16 points, 13 assists and six rebounds, and the Los Angeles Clippers routed the New York Knicks 116-88 on Friday night.

headline.print_headline: Jordan, Paul Help Clippers Coast Past Knicks, 116-88
